maintext:
HARRISBURG, Pa. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Thursday afternoon’s drawing of the Pennsylvania Lottery’s “Pick 5 Day” game were:
3-5-0-3-5, Wild: 2
(three, five, zero, three, five; Wild: two)
